name: Kyedae
description:
Kyedae

Twitch streamer - 2023 Valorant Streamer of the Year

I put this together to celebrate Kyedae's victory in the 2023 Streamer Awards as the Valorant Streamer of the Year. Kyedae has been diagnosed with Acute Myeloid Leukemia so we wish her all the best during her treatment and recovery.

Don't buy me a beer this time, please send donations to the American Cancer Society instead.

[ SDv1.4, 5e-03, 2600 steps, 0.196 ]
